prod.full_name: Jordan 1 Retro High Light Army Rust Shadow Patina
prod.path: Home/Sneakers/Air Jordan/1/High/Jordan 1 Retro High Light Army Rust Shadow Patina
prod.desciption:
The Air Jordan 1 Patina features a black leather upper with Light Army suede and copper-finished leather overlays. A mint Nike Air logo patch is stitched atop a black nylon tongue, adding a hit of color to the otherwise earth tone colorway.

The Air Jordan 1 Patina released in May of 2021 and retailed for $170.
